{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"89030df6a0","title":"我那些看法谈不到是犯罪","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"65a2abb441","index":0,"year":1969,"month":11,"day":3,"articleId":"89030df6a0"}],"tags":[{"id":"3aaab89c2a","name":"刘少奇","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"582ed43853","name":"张志新"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c74b116212","type":"title","text":"我那些看法谈不到是犯罪*","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"2e755724c3","type":"authors","text":"张志新","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"b385ca918c","type":"paragraph","text":"*这是张志新同志在管教所四次受审记录的摘要。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"3a41c88551","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六九年十一月三日第一次审讯记录","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"477f2b68b2","type":"paragraph","text":"审判员(以下简称为“审”)，到后(指到管教所后)有什么想法，对个人问题怎样认识？","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"72cb972151","type":"paragraph","text":"张志新(以下简称为“张”)：  (一九六九年)九月二十四日批斗后逮捕来的，怎样构成犯罪，我未想通。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"7a61d5acd3","type":"paragraph","text":"审：你“劲”别在哪里？","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"4a38ba4ea5","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我讲的那些都是向组织交代的，在群众中未散布。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"c652a7bc0c","type":"paragraph","text":"审，你在群众(居民)中散布过没有？","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"d08e25d838","type":"paragraph","text":"张，我没有。有些是认识错误，有些是不清楚的。有的是个人看法。“九大”后有些是犯罪的，有的未解决，坚持自己的观点。问题的由来，是由于对“文化大革命”两条路线[斗争的看法]。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"b0c10eae15","type":"paragraph","text":"审：你[思想]怎样产生的？","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"0e94a7bd84","type":"paragraph","text":"张：大量的主要是“文化大革命”中产生的，追溯得更远就是参加工作(以后)，特别到沈阳，工作便利看到些材料。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"a08d88fee9","type":"paragraph","text":"审：到这里来是帮助继续改造，但必须低头认罪。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"130305f8d8","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我来后集中考虑错在哪里，这条件很好，我过去没有很好学习，过去对路线斗争也不了解，产生怀疑、对立，坚持自己观点，是反动思想基础。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"7103f22903","type":"paragraph","text":"审：用主席哲学思想挖自己为什么产生这个问题，必须跳出个人立场，站到人民立场上来。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"6f58e29914","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我很想做这方面工作，怎样走过来的，错在哪里。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"2f71669ae3","type":"paragraph","text":"审：对你采取行动，有什么抵触情绪？","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"b49e174d08","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我没有对立情绪，对十二大队也没有对立情绪。","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"4249dcad63","type":"paragraph","text":"审：没有对立情绪，这想法是不对的，","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"d475529864","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我没有对立情绪，还很想他们。感到我对，又捕了我，这是矛盾。","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"73e294a070","type":"paragraph","text":"审：“十六条”是对还是错？","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"26d9ad3fb8","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我未得出结论。","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"5b04ed31ff","type":"paragraph","text":"审：对无产阶级司令部是拥护还是反对？","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"9465576f63","type":"paragraph","text":"张，我只是对无产阶级司令部有些怀疑，看法，可以保留。无产阶级司令部号召，我按干校布置去做，只是在一定会上讲，写了自己的观点。","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"a0689671fc","type":"paragraph","text":"审：现在不是错不错，作为思想认识是可以的。到这来不是错不错，而是犯罪的。不管你说或写，都是反动的。公开喊反动口号还要加重处刑。","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"209f7286cd","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我是在一定会议上——十二大队让我讲的。我对构成资产阶级反动路线不清楚。","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"b5fcad6e88","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六九年十二月二十七日第二次审讯记录","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"1b1a2fe100","type":"paragraph","text":"审：你对你的罪行怎么认识？还有什么罪行？","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"2532adf7e3","type":"paragraph","text":"张：还有攻击以毛主席为首林×××为副的无产阶级司令部的其他成员，如江青，对这场无产阶级文化大革命的性质和无产阶级革命路线。(原文如此——编者注)再就是为刘少奇为首的所谓资产阶级司令部翻案。","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"5ac61da5ec","type":"paragraph","text":"一九七○年一月三日第三次审讯记录","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"65a7d8ceba","type":"paragraph","text":"审：你为什么这样嚣张攻击伟大领袖毛主席和林×××？","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"eec97f2cc7","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我这不是攻击，这是我的看法。","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"81e93a50a2","type":"paragraph","text":"审：你这是看法吗？你这是想达到反革命目的。","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"d6be4e78a3","type":"paragraph","text":"张：你说我要达到反革命目的，哪条是？","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"82b8dce564","type":"paragraph","text":"审：我问你！","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"bc631b1bbd","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我这不是达到反革命目的，是我的看法。","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"67f40fcd31","type":"paragraph","text":"审：这是反对社会主义道路！","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"852c660835","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我哪一条反对社会主义道路？","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"381fc55d35","type":"paragraph","text":"审，你对伟大的中国共产党是攻击是拥护？","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"c9b7705ee3","type":"paragraph","text":"张，我这不是攻击，我是一个共产党员，提出我的看法，我认为是符合原则。","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"fdef43667d","type":"paragraph","text":"审：你是站在刘少奇的立场上，由于你的立场不同，所以你进行攻击和污蔑。你是一个反革命，所以你就攻击无产阶级司令部！","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"5901371c16","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我是用马克思列宁主义观点来看待的。","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"511520d191","type":"paragraph","text":"审：张志新，对你的罪行怎样认识？","index":42,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"15c30815ed","type":"paragraph","text":"张：通过我学习，谈不到罪行。","index":43,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"c46aedcf5f","type":"paragraph","text":"审：叫你说究竟犯了什么罪？","index":44,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"1f1dae591a","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我那些看法谈不到是犯罪。","index":45,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"5d7fbc5add","type":"paragraph","text":"审：你不想改造了？","index":46,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"d19c6c957d","type":"paragraph","text":"张：以前我还想过，老实点说现在不考虑了。","index":47,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"e08527e3b5","type":"paragraph","text":"审：我们希望你应当考虑你的前途！","index":48,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"6a4277bd30","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我没有什么考虑的，离开了党那就没有个人的前途，谈不上个人的前途问题。","index":49,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"24a4975d7b","type":"paragraph","text":"审：谁叫你脱离党的领导了？","index":50,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"4a1c05f1cc","type":"paragraph","text":"张：一个党员不过党的生活那是什么党？三年文化大革命没有过生活嘛！","index":51,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"dec7f96064","type":"paragraph","text":"审：你过去写交待材料里有右派言论，对你有影响，你讲一下！","index":52,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"4079a231ca","type":"paragraph","text":"张：叫我挖根源叫我从这方面找影响。绝对民主，绝对自由，资产阶级的民主自由是超阶级的自由。","index":53,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"0007511d7e","type":"paragraph","text":"审：你是不是要超阶级(的)民主自由？","index":54,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"520d5bba9e","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我不需要那些，我是共产党员。","index":55,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"4a8692b619","type":"paragraph","text":"审：张志新，你今后想怎样办？能不能想挖犯罪根源？","index":56,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"8f91a76ba8","type":"paragraph","text":"张：从我个人来讲没有什么可挖的，我讲的那些是对的。","index":57,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"8b9e896d00","type":"paragraph","text":"审：你和党有什么阶级仇恨？","index":58,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"ec15e0998f","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我没有，我是共产党员。","index":59,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"24d9521abb","type":"paragraph","text":"一九七○年二月三日第四次审讯记录","index":60,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"a00cb7712a","type":"paragraph","text":"审：你叫张志新吗？","index":61,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"1e742daf0d","type":"paragraph","text":"张：是。","index":62,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"889b36e947","type":"paragraph","text":"审：最近你有什么活思想？","index":63,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"3c1737b58b","type":"paragraph","text":"张：最近身体不好，我是怎么想的我就怎么讲，我是怎么个决心我也向组织讲清楚。我希望我的问题尽早搞清。","index":64,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"8ee6f9ba33","type":"paragraph","text":"审：你对你的罪行怎么认识的？你站在哪个立场上？","index":65,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"eb7a7f462d","type":"paragraph","text":"张：过去是想组织上服从，思想上保留。我脑子里的概念，无产阶级司令部不是“九大”以后的。我同意以前的毛泽东思想……","index":66,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"45c340ae76","type":"paragraph","text":"审：你站在什么立场上，你是站在无产阶级立场上，还是站在刘少奇资产阶级司令部立场上？","index":67,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"639acb2607","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我要找党，找真正的共产党。","index":68,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"b107aad97a","type":"paragraph","text":"审：谁是你真正的党？你准备怎么办？你想走什么路？一条是变过来，一条是变过去，这两条路你继续考虑。","index":69,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"},{"id":"f6da4f6527","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我不需要两条道路，我只有一条道路，就是马克思列宁主义真理的道路。","index":70,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0"}],"page":{"id":"6cb75116f9","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"89030df6a0","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}